## Biography

Stephen James Curry is widely considered the greatest shooter in NBA history and one of the most transformative players basketball has ever seen. Born in Akron, Ohio in 1988, he was drafted 7th overall by the Golden State Warriors in 2009 and spent 15 seasons transforming them into a dynasty. His greatest impact is on the sport itself: his extraordinary shooting range forced NBA defenses to completely reorganize, which changed how basketball is taught, trained, and played at every level worldwid...

